Subject: [PATCH] Revert "Bug 1333826 - Remove the make-sdk build target, the
 INSTALL_SDK variable, and all the supporting packager/upload machinery,
 r=mshal"

This reverts commit 4e6e8077298a31d44afdc4068a5709b69a25cf3a.

Signed-off-by: Pavel Tumakaev <p.tumakaev@omprussia.ru>
---
